Sentencas: Ni and Mo were added to ferritic stainless steel to improve the properties of the oxidation, electrical conductivity and Cr evaporation rate.
Titulo: Effect of Ni-Mo addition on cyclic and isothermal oxidation resistance and electrical behavior of ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: The purpose of making this alloy was for application in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) interconnect.
Titulo: Effect of Ni-Mo addition on cyclic and isothermal oxidation resistance and electrical behavior of ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: Therefore, the cyclic and isothermal oxidation tests were performed and the area-specific resistance (ASR) and the Cr evaporation rate were investigated.
Titulo: Effect of Ni-Mo addition on cyclic and isothermal oxidation resistance and electrical behavior of ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: The microstructure was discussed by scanning electron microscope (SEM).
Titulo: Effect of Ni-Mo addition on cyclic and isothermal oxidation resistance and electrical behavior of ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: Glow discharge spectrometry (GDS) and X-ray were used for elemental and phase analysis, respectively.
Titulo: Effect of Ni-Mo addition on cyclic and isothermal oxidation resistance and electrical behavior of ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: The addition of 3 wt% Mo reduced the oxidation rate and the Cr evaporation resistance by the formation of Laves-phase in oxide/metal interface.
Titulo: Effect of Ni-Mo addition on cyclic and isothermal oxidation resistance and electrical behavior of ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: By reducing the activity of Fe in the steel, Mo was prevented outward diffusion of cations and anion diffusivity.
Titulo: Effect of Ni-Mo addition on cyclic and isothermal oxidation resistance and electrical behavior of ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: Furthermore, Mo improved the electrical conductivity by filling the gaps and voids in the oxide/metal interface.
Titulo: Effect of Ni-Mo addition on cyclic and isothermal oxidation resistance and electrical behavior of ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: The addition of 2 wt% Ni reduced the distribution of Laves-phase particles in substrate and the particles were moved to side oxide/metal interface and neighboring areas to it.
Titulo: Effect of Ni-Mo addition on cyclic and isothermal oxidation resistance and electrical behavior of ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect

Sentencas: Ni also improved the oxidation resistance and electrical conductivity in the steel.
Titulo: Effect of Ni-Mo addition on cyclic and isothermal oxidation resistance and electrical behavior of ferritic stainless steel for SOFCs interconnect
